channel.title: Delta Project Development [Hurry]
channel.description:
[quote="Encryption, post:1, topic:338116"][font=impact][size=4]Home Sweet Home![/size][/font] [img]http://i40.tinypic.com/sbr61w.png[/img]
[size=3]Home In Mortanyia, lots of shops great economy and skills to train. You currently don't see all the yellow dots cause the mini map was removed in the picture. [/size]
[font=impact][size=4]Chill Zone Where everyone get to hang out and talk, mostly staff zone and donator passageways...[/size][/font] [img]http://i44.tinypic.com/34j7tp1.png[/img]
[size=3]Trade Donator shops (Message: "You peeked in the shop, then realized you need to donate") Those to NPC's are Donator shops Only. Hero's Guild Is Chill Zone. Thievery for staff and donators on gem stall... Ladder Takes you to donator train (Message: "Only donators may enter, Below you see penguins?")[/size]
[font=impact][size=4]Some Featured Mini's.[/size][/font] [img]http://i39.tinypic.com/35d9pci.png[/img]
[size=3]Great mini's to enjoy, Jad is 63 waves. Good Luck lol.[/size]
[font=impact][size=4]A Wall Of Features![/size][/font] [img]http://i41.tinypic.com/2urqjoi.png[/img]
[size=3]Beer store at Home (The Big Pub In Mortanyia lol) All the rares are donator only, and hard to get drops by (Penguins) Mini map of Penguin Lair (Where the ladder takes you). Train teleport, with great destinations to try out. Red portal takes you to fight in God wars (General Graardor) [/size]
[font=impact][size=4]More Information![/font]
[font=times new roman][size=3]I hope you all liked this, and there are more updates coming by. There Are much more features then you've seen in the pictures. There are great commands, that are extremely useful. Great Economy: Mod, Admins, Have to train there stats like the rest. (Nothing easier for them at all) Each Item is highly priced and a great amount of money taken from stalls to buy items.
The ::pickup is removed due to ruining the economy if used lawl. [/size]
[size=14pt]Print: If you want help develop a great economy server add my msn here.. Msn: Volunteer09@hotmail.com[/size][/quote]
[quote="Encryption, post:10, topic:338116"]Rares are basically maxed cash, and if they happened to get it. They'd be able to get one. It'll take them a long time, and them only being donators because there not available to anyone.
The stall(s) give a low money count, and it's only 500k per swipe at it.
Customs: D Claws, D Plate
Big deal that's what people are looking forward too these days.[/quote]
You want in on this PM me and application in my in box or add me: volunteer09@hotmail.com
